\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26019fd2a1d51deb092e0b9ee48d49ab8368be3a","tid":1634304,"uid":226896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"呢招得！我周圍去大大聲講電話先！"},{"pid":"2ae8f7792f6467c213a35276650ab04a81a85758","tid":1634304,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"有冇人用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8c2863c6dfeeb8a50c0430146166c2db97347f","tid":1634304,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n［圍觀師第一次出動］今晚去黨鐵站 （文宣好機會）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}